屆選舉的候選人提供進一步資料，以確認他們的參選資格，社會對此有不少討論，甚至質疑。<br />\n <br />\n局方重申，根據現行選舉條例，選舉主任有權依法決定個別報名的參選人符合候選資格與否。在確認候選人的參選資格前，選舉主任會按情況諮詢律政司、政制及內地事務局等的意見，並在需要時按《選舉管理委員會（選舉程序）（立法會）規例》要求參選人提供其認為適當的額外資料，以令其信納候選人有資格獲提名或該項提名為有效。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:13:04.000Z","msg":"而且張相應該係首先由政府網站自己公開&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/12/P2020071000472.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F12%2FP2020071000472.htm&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=8457db8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/12/P2020071000472.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"政府可以話無授權你咁用，違反私隱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但明明係政府起人底先喎<br />\n選舉主任問咁撚多問題，算唔算起人底？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:58:06.000Z","msg":"冇肖像權,又唔係偷拍佢私生活<br />\n應該唔會犯咩私隱法<br />\n利申:唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376274c4df281e443b3ee964af983fe5fbefdfdd","tid":2128080,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:58:12.000Z","msg":"咁又犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32af42ccb30515a6fc23d4d2d82164e7392ccea1","tid":2128080,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4371e57150b34f5655dc2c3922914d2e0eac5f5","tid":2128080,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a1a2cb51f3c9efd02693214ede71c3624b551f2","tid":2128080,"uid":89683,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"42c06c039f82b4a0d8a8326db9f91c27da1020d6","tid":2128080,"uid":266170,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:13:04.000Z","msg":"而且張相應該係首先由政府網站自己公開&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/12/P2020071000472.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lih